Package: ggjbrowse
Title: ggplot2 Geoms for Genomic Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JBrowse", "Team", , "jbrowse@gmod.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2 geoms and scales for creating JBrowse-style genomic
    visualizations. Includes geoms for gene tracks, coverage plots, variant
    displays, and multi-track assemblies. Designed to work seamlessly with
    jbrowseR for reproducible genomic analysis.
